timeline.body:
the error message in `putSource` needs to be updated:
```java
      existing.source.canUpgradeTo(dataSource).ifPresent(msg -> {
        throw new KsqlException("Cannot REPLACE data source: " + msg);
      });
```
We could either make it more generic, or pass in more details in the `putSource` method to correctly display `ALTER` or `REPLACE`

